high_descs: Turn around, head to the watch on the desk, to the far left.
Pick up the watch on the desk.
Bring the watch over to the bowl on the left side of the desk.
Put the watch in the bowl on the desk.
Pick up the bowl with watch on the desk.
Bring the bowl to the left most side of the desk.
Put the bowl with watch in the shelf under the left desk.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a watch in it on the shelf.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the wooden desk on the left.
Pick up the watch from the middle of the desk.
Turn around, hang a right at the wall and turn right to face the wooden desk.
Put the watch inside the gray bowl in the middle of the desk.
Pick up the gray bowl with the watch from the middle of the desk.
Turn left and hang a right at the wall to face the desk next to the chair.
Put the bowl with the watch on the shelf under the left side of the desk top.
anns.task_desc: Place a bowl with a watch on a shelf.

high_descs: Turn around and walk forward, then hang a left and walk up to the wooden desk.
Pick up the watch off of the wooden desk.
Turn around and walk up to the wall, then turn right and walk forward, turn right to face the wooden desk.
Put the watch in the grey bowl on the desk.
Pick up the grey bowl with the watch in it off of the desk.
Turn left and walk towards the wall, then turn right to face the left end of the wooden desk.
Put the grey bowl with the watch in it on the shelf below the wooden desk.
anns.task_desc: Put a grey bowl with a watch in it on a shelf.
